All operational plans submitted under this section must comply with the provisions of:
* this Act;
* any regulations made under this Act;
* any condition imposed on the licence or permit to
* any applicable Code of Practice approved under this

The forestry application fee shall comprise:
* a nominal fixed amount to cover the administration
* an amount charged at a rate fixed by written Order to
* a reafforestation levy;
* a research levy;

(1) Holders of licences and permits granted under this Act shall pay levies fixed by regulations made under this Act which may be in the nature of:
* an environmental levy.
* any law relating to the declaration or management of
* any provision of any management plan approved
* protecting the biodiversity of Samoa;
* providing protection for endangered species;
